      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=400&rangeEnd=420",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=400&rangeEnd=420"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_9_79200-79297",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "79200-79297",
      "markText": "“是的，你把我占有了，我是你的人。”她把他的手紧贴在胸口，终于说。 “这个当然！”他说，“我们活一天，就应该这样过一天，这一点我现在明白了。”",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=79200&rangeEnd=79297",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=79200&rangeEnd=79297"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_6_16878-16909",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16878-16909",
      "markText": "他们各人都以为自己所过的是唯一正确的生活，而别人却在虚度年华。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16878&rangeEnd=16909",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16878&rangeEnd=16909"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_6_19995-20025",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "19995-20025",
      "markText": "“忙于纸上谈兵。不过你干这种事是很有才能的。”列文补了一句。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19995&rangeEnd=20025",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=19995&rangeEnd=20025"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_7_31885-31936",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "31885-31936",
      "markText": "最初一刹那，卡列宁仿佛对自己的鼾声感到吃惊，停止了；但呼吸了两下以后，鼾声就又更加均匀而平静地响起来。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=31885&rangeEnd=31936",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=31885&rangeEnd=31936"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_8_74049-74104",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "74049-74104",
      "markText": "她知道，不论他对她说什么，他都不会把他的全部想法告诉她。她明白，她的最后一线希望落空了。这不是她所期待的局面。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=74049&rangeEnd=74104",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=74049&rangeEnd=74104"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_12_22014-22030",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "22014-22030",
      "markText": "因为照他看来，吉蒂已经爱上他了。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=22014&rangeEnd=22030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=22014&rangeEnd=22030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_11_6453-6493",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6453-6493",
      "markText": "列文微微一笑。一想到妻子不会让他去打猎，他觉得很好玩，他情愿从此放弃猎熊的乐趣。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6453&rangeEnd=6493",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6453&rangeEnd=6493"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_4_4364-4445",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4364-4445",
      "markText": "人总是有时是这样的，有时是另一样的；有时坚强，有时软弱；有时明理，有时错乱；有时善良，有时凶恶。人不是一个确定的常数，而是某种变化着的，有时堕落、有时向上的东西。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4364&rangeEnd=4445",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4364&rangeEnd=4445"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_6_13745-13818",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13745-13818",
      "markText": "他生活放荡，年资不高，却在莫斯科官厅里担任一个体面而且俸金优厚的官职。这个位置他是通过妹妹安娜的丈夫阿历克赛·阿历山德罗维奇·卡列宁的关系谋得的。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13745&rangeEnd=13818",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13745&rangeEnd=13818"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_6_22294-22362",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "22294-22362",
      "markText": "但列文正在热恋中，他觉得吉蒂是个十全十美的姑娘，是下凡的仙女，他自己则是个庸夫俗子，因此他简直不敢想象，别人和她本人会认为他能高攀得上。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=22294&rangeEnd=22362",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=22294&rangeEnd=22362"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_7_76158-76249",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "76158-76249",
      "markText": "他同安娜关系中一切痛苦的事，他们谈话后所留下的前途茫茫的感觉，都从他的头脑里消失了。现在他高兴而激动地想着赛马，想到他一定能赶上比赛。今夜快乐的约会，只偶尔像火花一样在他头脑里闪过。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=76158&rangeEnd=76249",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=76158&rangeEnd=76249"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_8_65504-65604",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "65504-65604",
      "markText": "既然伏伦斯基确信爱情就是他的幸福，情愿为恋爱牺牲功名，至少认为自己已经抱定这样的宗旨，他也就不妒忌谢普霍夫斯科依了，也不因为他回到团里不先来看他而生气。谢普霍夫斯科依是他的好朋友，这次回来他自然高兴。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=65504&rangeEnd=65604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=65504&rangeEnd=65604"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_9_44398-44433",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "44398-44433",
      "markText": "他们谈话时什么都谈到了。吉蒂说她爱他，她会告诉爸爸妈妈他明天早晨要来。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=44398&rangeEnd=44433",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=44398&rangeEnd=44433"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_6_14686-14703",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14686-14703",
      "markText": "随便，从来不卖力，也从来不犯错误。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14686&rangeEnd=14703",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14686&rangeEnd=14703"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096126_6_101239-101297",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "101239-101297",
      "markText": "“不过，安娜，我对你说句实话，我不太赞成吉蒂这门婚事。要是他伏伦斯基一天里就会对你发生爱情，这门婚事还是吹掉的好。”",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096126&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=101239&rangeEnd=101297",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e7326d0813ab8c0cg0164c3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=101239&rangeEnd=101297"
